{"type":"message","id":"61e578b8","parentId":"ab53ad6d","timestamp":"2026-04-06T00:10:35.907Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"sqlite3 is not installed but libsqlite3-0 is. Let me try using a node script to query the db, or just report what I've found.\n\nLet me summarize what I've found:\n\n1. **lcm.db** - SQLite database storing sessions and messages. Tables include:\n   - `messages` - message content\n   - `sessions` - session data\n   - `context_items` - context management\n   - `summary_*` tables - for conversation summarization\n\n2. **memory-lancedb** - LanceDB vector storage for memories at `~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb-pro/memories.lance/`\n\n3. **openviking** - Context engine running on `localhost:1933` with remote mode enabled\n\n4. **Workspace files** - Plain text files in `~/.openclaw/workspace/` including:\n   - AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, USER.md, etc.\n   - memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md files\n   - MEMORY.md\n\nThe issue is likely that when HALEI changed the OpenViking database, it may have reset or changed something. OpenViking is being used as the context engine, which handles the conversation context and memory.\n\nLet me explain what I found to HALEI.","thinkingSignature":"826d79432b0537385022da810ee475c93316342ef89053c09ad1d82c222036d6"},{"type":"text","text":"找到原因了。\n\n**当前存储架构：**\n\n| 组件 | 路径 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **lcm.db** | `~/.openclaw/lcm.db` | SQLite，记录 sessions 和 messages |\n| **LanceDB** | `~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb-pro/memories.lance/` | 向量记忆存储 |\n| **Workspace 文件** | `~/.openclaw/workspace/*.md` | 纯文本记忆文件（AGENTS.md、SOUL.md、memory/ 等） |\n| **OpenViking** | `localhost:1933` (remote 模式) | 上下文引擎（context engine） |\n\n**关键配置：**\n```json\n\"memory\": \"memory-lancedb\",\n\"contextEngine\": \"openviking\"\n```\n\nOpenViking 正在以 **remote 模式** 连接到 `http://localhost:1933`，API Key 是 `openviking2024`。\n\n**问题推测：**\n你换了 OpenViking 的数据库，但 OpenViking 目前是 remote 模式连接本地服务。如果新数据库和旧数据库不兼容，或者 OpenViking 服务本身出了问题，就可能导致上下文丢失。\n\n**建议检查：**\n1. OpenViking 服务是否正常运行？`curl http://localhost:1933/health`\n2. 换数据库后 OpenViking 的记忆是否还在？\n3. LanceDB 的 `memories.lance` 数据是否完整？\n\n要我去检查 OpenViking 的状态，或者帮你看看 LanceDB 里有什么记忆数据吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5285,"output":575,"cacheRead":12505,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18365,"cost":{"input":0.0015854999999999999,"output":0.00069,"cacheRead":0.0007503,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0030257999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775434223010,"responseId":"06222cef2a7a88d2a506129be52338ae"}}
