{"type":"message","id":"b2249862","parentId":"cb4501b9","timestamp":"2026-04-06T01:56:46.860Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah, the user is saying they haven't given me their GitHub account yet. I need to ask them to provide their GitHub credentials or help me authenticate with GitHub so I can create the repository.","thinkingSignature":"95b1369d5b7c211054697103f42d4047d3d62818c905b14d08bc698d08d2d8a6"},{"type":"text","text":"那先要把你的 GitHub 账号授权给我。你有几种方式：\n\n1. **给我 GitHub Personal Access Token**（推荐，最简单）\n   - 去 GitHub → Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → Generate new token\n   - 需要勾选 `repo` 权限\n\n2. **临时授权 CLI**：装好 `gh` 后，你跑一遍 `gh auth login`，它会引导你完成 OAuth 授权\n\n你想用哪种方式？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":140,"cacheRead":18331,"cacheWrite":949,"totalTokens":19459,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.000168,"cacheRead":0.0010998599999999998,"cacheWrite":0.000355875,"total":0.001635435}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775440601292,"responseId":"062245d9c5bc694039ef38ecd2274bbf"}}
