{"type":"message","id":"dfd94718","parentId":"dd20bbad","timestamp":"2026-04-06T02:02:21.599Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/0f6c58b9-6823-4c00-a04b-da73c6705a31.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/0f6c58b9-6823-4c00-a04b-da73c6705a31.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-04-06 10:01:15 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b5205706b5cacc3b1ff0ec047b6c, image, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5205706b5cacc3b1ff0ec047b6c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 10:01 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/0f6c58b9-6823-4c00-a04b-da73c6705a31.jpg"}],"timestamp":1775440941465}}
