{"type":"message","id":"d165d279","parentId":"b71675ae","timestamp":"2026-04-06T02:05:09.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, it seems the authentication didn't complete or wasn't saved. Let me check if there's a different gh auth status or if we need to try again. Let me also check if the token might be stored somewhere.","thinkingSignature":"5249c5d78bd9e3637ef9654dd27433fb4f6b0e071d07ba545e45bb3aba0cfc6f"},{"type":"text","text":"没成功。回到服务器终端，按 Enter 跳过浏览器，然后在终端里选 **Token** 方式登录：\n\n```bash\ngh auth login\n```\n\n1. 选择 `Login with a web browser` 后会卡住——换这个：\n2. 选 `Paste a token`\n\n然后去 GitHub 网页生成 token：\n- GitHub → Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → **Generate new token (classic)**\n- 勾选 `repo` 权限\n- 生成后复制 token，在终端粘贴\n\n或者你直接把 token 发给我，我直接用 `gh api` 创建仓库。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9043,"output":167,"cacheRead":12505,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21715,"cost":{"input":0.0027129,"output":0.0002004,"cacheRead":0.0007503,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0036635999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775441101196,"responseId":"062247cdfc6ce1888e9275a67140a9ca"}}
