{"type":"message","id":"0c078566","parentId":"8d2bc1bb","timestamp":"2026-04-06T02:21:02.085Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-06 10:20:56 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b5205c6b368a8c33698b3b824bc5]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5205c6b368a8c33698b3b824bc5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 10:20 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n备份你openclaw 都应该备份啥，咱先沟通一下，在执行"}],"timestamp":1775442062076}}
{"type":"message","id":"dadefb82","parentId":"0c078566","timestamp":"2026-04-06T02:21:15.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to discuss what to back up before proceeding. Let me think about what OpenClaw data is important to back up:\n\n1. **Workspace files** - AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, USER.md, IDENTITY.md, TOOLS.md, MEMORY.md, daily memory files\n2. **Configuration** - openclaw.json (the main config)\n3. **Credentials** - credentials/ directory\n4. **Extensions** - extensions/ (though these can be reinstalled)\n5. **lcm.db** - SQLite database with session/message history\n6. **memory/lancedb-pro/** - Vector memory database\n7. **tasks/runs.sqlite** - Task runs\n\n\n8. **flows/registry.sqlite** - Flow registry\n9. **agents/** - Agent configurations\n10. **cron/** - Cron jobs\n11. **Identity** - identity/ directory\n\nThe main things worth preserving are the workspace and memory files since they contain my context and identity, the configuration and credentials, the databases storing session history and vector memory, and any custom agents or cron configurations. Extensions can generally be reinstalled from their sources, and while I could back up everything, focusing on these key areas keeps the backup manageable and avoids including replaceable components.","thinkingSignature":"0b21a4f62724f265c5ca66dcf0cffd6dc234b763286e5b1bf3318b77b959a530"},{"type":"text","text":"备份前先对齐一下。OpenClaw 的数据大致分这几类：\n\n**必须备份（不可恢复）：**\n| 路径 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| `workspace/*.md` | 我的记忆文件（MEMORY.md、SOUL.md、memory/ 日记等） |\n| `openclaw.json` | 主配置文件 |\n| `credentials/` | 第三方 API keys、tokens |\n| `identity/` | 身份配置 |\n\n**建议备份：**\n| 路径 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| `lcm.db` | 聊天记录、sessions 历史 |\n| `memory/lancedb-pro/` | 向量记忆数据库 |\n| `agents/` | 自定义 Agent 配置 |\n| `cron/` | 定时任务配置 |\n\n**可跳过（可重新安装）：**\n- `extensions/` — npm 包，可从源码重新安装\n- `logs/` — 日志文件\n\n你想全量备份，还是先只备份核心的记忆和配置？我建议先备份核心的，extensions 不备份（太大且可重新安装）。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":479,"cacheRead":21681,"cacheWrite":681,"totalTokens":22880,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0005748,"cacheRead":0.0013008599999999998,"cacheWrite":0.000255375,"total":0.0021427349999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775442062082,"responseId":"06224b8eb9f318b4ef74040bcb26ce7f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0fb1628","parentId":"dadefb82","timestamp":"2026-04-06T02:36:50.379Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-06 10:35:44 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b5205f13b6cb4c435bd448f07c4f, post]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5205f13b6cb4c435bd448f07c4f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 10:35 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n**1. 安全提醒（重中之重）**\n\n\n- **credentials/**** 绝对不能直接上传 GitHub 公开仓库**，必须：\n\n  a. 用.gitignore排除该目录，或\n\n  b. 加密后备份，或\n\n  c. 仅备份到私有仓库并严格控制权限\n\n\n\n\n- 建议在备份时单独处理credentials/，避免密钥泄露\n\n\n**2. 备份策略优化**\n\n\n- **增量备份**：核心文件（workspace/、openclaw.json）每日自动备份，大文件（lancedb-pro/）每周全量备份"}],"timestamp":1775443010182}}
{"type":"message","id":"160f06c5","parentId":"c0fb1628","timestamp":"2026-04-06T02:37:01.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is giving me a safety reminder about backing up credentials. They're saying:\n1. Never upload credentials/ to a public GitHub repo - must use .gitignore, encrypt, or use private repo with strict permissions\n2. Backup strategy: daily incremental for core files (workspace/, openclaw.json), weekly full backup for large files (lancedb-pro/)\n\nThey're absolutely right about the security concern. I should acknowledge this and then propose a plan that:\n1. Creates a .gitignore to exclude credentials/\n2. Uses the private repo we just created\n3. Sets up a backup strategy\n\nLet me confirm I understand and then ask if they want me to proceed with this backup plan.","thinkingSignature":"98db578dc3ded7aefd527babb0799bbad622fa96d7e8b39d0afdb9463a38b0c2"},{"type":"text","text":"完全正确。credentials/ 必须排除。\n\n那备份方案：\n\n**Step 1：建 .gitignore（排除敏感文件）**\n```\ncredentials/\nextensions/\nlogs/\n*.db\n*.db-shm\n*.db-wal\nmemory/lancedb-pro/\nsubagents/\ntasks/\n```\n\n**Step 2：备份内容**\n- `workspace/` — 记忆文件\n- `openclaw.json` — 配置\n- `agents/` — Agent 配置\n- `cron/` — 定时任务\n- `skills/` — 自定义 skills\n- `.env` 类配置文件（不含密钥的模板）\n\n**Step 3：加密 credentials（可选后续做）**\n\n要按这个方案执行吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":288,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":22972,"totalTokens":23299,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0003456,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0086145,"total":0.0089718}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775443010195,"responseId":"06224f4379f39f9ea8ef6589353d6845"}}
