{"type":"message","id":"07e5c4a1","parentId":"88ec5f56","timestamp":"2026-04-06T02:45:43.786Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's sensitive data in `openclaw.json`:\n- WeChat passwords/tokens\n- API keys for OpenAI/LanceDB\n- OpenViking API key\n\nI should exclude these files from the backup. Let me update the .gitignore to include `exec-approvals.json`, `openviking.env`, and maybe `openclaw.json` (or at least the version with credentials).\n\nActually, for a backup, I should:\n1. Keep the file structure but mask/remove sensitive data\n2. Or create a \"template\" version without secrets\n\nThe safest approach: exclude files with credentials and only backup non-sensitive config structure.\n\nLet me update .gitignore and then commit what's safe.","thinkingSignature":"ef89ca97a165c38c2d4eea816d4bb2a991e8ede23b96162061ed2031aaa03bb2"},{"type":"text","text":"发现敏感数据。要排除这些文件：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cf6mefxyoz0y_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Credentials - NEVER backup\ncredentials/\n*.pem\n*.key\n*.crt\n\n# Logs\nlogs/\n\n# Large databases\n*.db\n*.db-shm\n*.db-wal\n\n# LanceDB (too large, backup separately if needed)\nmemory/lancedb-pro/\n\n# Extensions (reinstallable via npm)\nextensions/\n\n# Subagents (runtime state)\nsubagents/\n\n# Task runs (temporary)\ntasks/runs.sqlite\n\n# Docker volumes\n*.volume\n\n# OS files\n.DS_Store\nThumbs.db\n\n# Temporary files\n*.tmp\n*.swp\n*~\n\n# Sensitive configs with tokens/keys\nexec-approvals.json\nopenviking.env\nopenclaw.json\nopenclaw.json.bak\nopenclaw.json.bak.1\nopenclaw.json.bak.2\nopenclaw.json.bak.3\nopenclaw.json.bak.4\nupdate-check.json\n","path":"/tmp/openclaw-backup/.gitignore"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17032,"output":383,"cacheRead":12505,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29920,"cost":{"input":0.0051096,"output":0.0004596,"cacheRead":0.0007503,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0063195}},"s