{"type":"message","id":"9b857a93","parentId":"5a43fe98","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:25:47.613Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-06 11:25:44 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b5206354dc0a0c43a8ab6bbcb53f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5206354dc0a0c43a8ab6bbcb53f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 11:25 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n已经看到了。后面备份是不是要使用 日期的形式进行文件夹分类备份呢"}],"timestamp":1775445947490}}
{"type":"message","id":"de7c58be","parentId":"9b857a93","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:26:02.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about future backups - whether we should organize them by date in folders. Let me think about this...\n\nCurrently the backup is just pushed to the main branch. For future incremental backups, we could:\n1. Use dated commits (git automatically timestamps)\n2. Create dated tags\n3. Create dated branches (e.g., backup/2026-04-06)\n\nSince it's git, commits already have timestamps. But if they want folder-based organization, we could structure it differently.\n\nActually, since this is a git repo, the natural approach would be:\n- Use git commits with dates (already done)\n- Use tags like `backup-2026-04-06`\n- Or use branches per date if they want folder-like isolation\n\nLet me ask what they prefer - the git-native approach (tags/branches) or folder-based structure.","thinkingSignature":"de2fef07bebac70c043713cca7b9e42033926bd1a99099d70eb12de2227f16df"},{"type":"text","text":"\nGit 本身已经是时间序列了（每次 commit 都有日期）。但如果你想要更清晰的版本管理，可以这样：\n\n**方案 A：打标签（推荐）**\n```bash\ngit tag backup-2026-04-06\ngit push --tags\n```\n→ 仓库里会显示每个备份点，一目了然\n\n**方案 B：按月份建文件夹**\n```\nopenclaw-backup/\n├── 2026-04/\n│   ├── openclaw.json\n│   ├── workspace/\n│   └── ...\n└── 2026-05/\n    └── ...\n```\n→ 文件系统式，但每次要全量复制，仓库会越来越大\n\n**我的建议：用方案 A（标签）**，每次备份只 push 增量，标签标记时间点。需要恢复时 `git checkout backup-2026-04-06` 就行。\n\n要我设置一个定时任务自动打标签备份吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":359,"cacheRead":40683,"cacheWrite":690,"totalTokens":41771,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.00043079999999999995,"cacheRead":0.0024409799999999997,"cacheWrite":0.00025875000000000003,"total":0.0031422299999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775445947497,"responseId":"06225abd877b1338feafc202408b6dd9"}}
