{"type":"message","id":"136efeb3","parentId":"37effa46","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:26:53.764Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Tag pushed. Now let me set up a cron job to automate the backup process. I'll create a script that:\n1. rsyncs the openclaw directory (with excludes)\n2. commits with date-based message\n3. pushes and tags with date\n\nLet me create this script and set up the cron job.","thinkingSignature":"146b01d33d0173ca23a1676bcd7bc05fe7b5b79d5161d0b247ef32ef884f06e9"},{"type":"text","text":"标签打好了。现在设个定时任务，每天自动备份：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uqcyoafac6ht_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw 自动备份脚本\n# 备份到 GitHub，添加日期标签\n\nset -e\n\nBACKUP_DIR=\"/tmp/openclaw-backup-git\"\nSOURCE_DIR=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nREPO=\"https://github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git\"\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n\n# 克隆仓库\nif [ -d \"$BACKUP_DIR\" ]; then\n    cd \"$BACKUP_DIR\"\n    git pull --quiet\nelse\n    git clone --depth 1 \"$REPO\" \"$BACKUP_DIR\"\n    cd \"$BACKUP_DIR\"\nfi\n\n# 同步文件（排除敏感文件）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='credentials' \\\n    --exclude='logs' \\\n    --exclude='*.db' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-shm' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-wal' \\\n    --exclude='extensions' \\\n    --exclude='subagents' \\\n    --exclude='tasks/runs.sqlite' \\\n    --exclude='memory/lancedb-pro' \\\n    --exclude='sessions/*.jsonl' \\\n    --exclude='auth-profiles.json' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_DIR/\" .\n\n# 脱敏 openclaw.json\nif [ -f openclaw.json ]; then\n    python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('openclaw.json') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\n# mask tokens\ndef mask(obj):\n    if isinstance(obj, dict):\n        for k in obj:\n            if k in ('token', 'apiKey', 'password', 'secret'):\n                obj[k] = '***REDACTED***'\n            else:\n                mask(obj[k])\n    elif isinstance(obj, list):\n        for i in obj:\n            mask(i)\nmask(d)\nwith open('openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2)\n\" 2>/dev/null || true\nfi\n\n# 提交\ngit add -A\nif git diff --cached --quiet; then\n    echo \"No changes to commit\"\nelse\n    git commit -m \"Backup $TODAY\"\n    git push --quiet\n    # 打标签\n    git tag -a \"backup-$TODAY\" -m \"Backup $TODAY\"\n    git push origin \"backup-$TODAY\" --quiet\n    echo \"Backup $TODAY done\"\nfi\n","path":"/tmp/openclaw-backup.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29530,"output":621,"cacheRead":12505,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42656,"cost":{"input":0.008858999999999999,"output":0.0007452,"cacheRead":0.0007503,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010354499999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775445999406,"responseId":"06225af03b85a04601cbb3f2e11ce21b"}}
