{"type":"message","id":"83c524dc","parentId":"cdbf6ec0","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:08:21.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the OpenViking data structure. Let me summarize what data is stored where.","thinkingSignature":"ac5ea4fdc896298e35c067026350c89ed772a30f7d3db75fa4fc09e0c106da79"},{"type":"text","text":"**OpenViking 存储结构（`~/.openviking/`）：**\n\n| 目录/文件 | 大小 | 内容 |\n|-----------|------|------|\n| `viking/default/session/` | 252K | **对话 session 数据**（消息历史、上下文） |\n| `viking/default/user/` | 72K | 用户相关数据 |\n| `viking/default/agent/` | 12K | Agent 配置 |\n| `viking/default/resources/` | 12K | 资源文件 |\n| `vectordb/context/` | 72K | **向量数据库**（embedding 索引） |\n| `_system/` | 4.1M | 系统数据 |\n| `bot/` | 16K | Bot 配置 |\n| `ov.conf` | 4K | 配置文件 |\n\n**简单说：**\n\nOpenViking 作为 **context engine** 存的是：\n- **对话上下文**（session 消息）\n- **向量索引**（用于语义搜索/记忆检索）\n- **Agent 配置**\n\nOpenClaw 的 **lcm.db**（SQLite）存的是：\n- sessions 列表\n- messages 元数据\n- 插件状态\n\n两者互为补充，OpenViking 负责\"记什么\"，lcm.db 负责\"怎么组织\"。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38402,"output":289,"cacheRead":12505,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51196,"cost":{"input":0.011520599999999999,"output":0.00034679999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0007503,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012617699999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775448492515,"responseId":"062264adc0077c3c0f5b3aaeabae7389"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7ad9fb7","parentId":"83c524dc","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:09:03.923Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-06 12:08:56 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b5207534b4d34c10bb0b273f99ab]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5207534b4d34c10bb0b273f99ab\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 12:08 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n那GitHub备份，没有备份到的数据是那个"}],"timestamp":1775448543903}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e4dd423","parentId":"a7ad9fb7","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:09:17.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking which data is NOT being backed up to GitHub. From the backup we did earlier, we excluded:\n- credentials/\n- logs/\n- *.db (lcm.db, flows/registry.sqlite, tasks/runs.sqlite)\n- *.db-shm, *.db-wal\n- memory/lancedb-pro/ (LanceDB)\n- extensions/\n- subagents/\n- tasks/runs.sqlite\n- sessions/*.jsonl (session log files)\n- auth-profiles.json\n- exec-approvals.json\n- openviking.env\n- openclaw.json (fully excluded because we couldn't decrypt it, but we should have had a sanitized version)\n\n\n- openclaw.json.bak* (backup configs)\n\nWe also skipped the OpenViking data entirely. So the main things not getting backed up are the actual message logs from sessions, the LanceDB vector memory store, the SQLite databases like lcm.db and registry, credentials files, and the OpenViking data directory. Since we already pushed to GitHub with the remote configured, we just need to add and push the tag.","thinkingSignature":"91a1a44c0ff0c90452764eb950496861fe1ab9ca8d13a88e3705f36df96a38c1"},{"type":"text","text":"已排除未备份的数据：\n\n| 数据 | 路径 | 未备份原因 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| **对话消息日志** | `sessions/*.jsonl` | 对话内容太大太敏感 |\n| **向量记忆库** | `memory/lancedb-pro/` | LanceDB 太大（几百MB+） |\n| **消息数据库** | `lcm.db` | SQLite 二进制 |\n| **流程注册** | `flows/registry.sqlite` | 同上 |\n| **凭证密钥** | `credentials/` | 安全考虑 |\n| **任务运行记录** | `tasks/runs.sqlite` | 临时数据 |\n| **OpenViking 数据** | `~/.openviking/` | 新数据，未加入备份 |\n\n**关键未备份：** OpenViking 的 session 和向量数据目前只在本地。如果要备份 OpenViking，可以把 `~/.openviking/` 也加到备份脚本里（只备份 `viking/default/` 和 `vectordb/`，排除 `_system/` 和 `bot/`）。要加吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":448,"cacheRead":49693,"cacheWrite":1658,"totalTokens":51838,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0005376,"cacheRead":0.0029815799999999997,"cacheWr