{"type":"message","id":"f8012f29","parentId":"6f142958","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:13:35.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clearer picture:- `agents/main/sessions/`: 5.1MB, 14 .jsonl files- `lcm.db`: 1.4MB- `media/`: 4.1MB\n- OpenViking: 4.6MB\n\nTotal that's not currently backed up:- sessions/*.jsonl: 5.1MB (14 files)\n- lcm.db: 1.4MB\n- media/: 4.1MB\n- OpenViking: 4.6MB\n\nThat's about 15MB additional. With the current 22MB backup, we'd be at ~37MB. That's still very manageable.\n\n\nFor a better strategy, I should back up the SQLite and JSONL files as binary data using Git LFS rather than trying to compress them, since they're already compressed. The `.jsonl.reset` and `.jsonl.deleted` files appear to be old session artifacts from before the migration, so those might not be necessary to include in the backup. The backup already contains:\n- workspace/ (memory files)\n- agents/main/product-selector/\n- agents/main/agent/\n- skills/\n- cron/\n- identity/\n\nWhat's missing:\n- agents/main/sessions/ (5.1MB, 14 files)\n- agents/tts/sessions/\n- flows/registry.sqlite\n- lcm.db\n- media/ (4.1MB)\n- OpenViking data (4.6MB)\n\nGitHub's free tier gives generous storage for private repos with no firm limits, so we're not constrained there. I should present a comprehensive backup strategy that includes everything and let them choose based on what matters most.","thinkingSignature":"e86579b9c3a208a66caa40f211506144d03bd91b19e1a2e412fda6ea51d81100"},{"type":"text","text":"现有数据体量：\n\n| 数据 | 大小 | 当前备份状态 |\n|------|------|------------|\n| 已有备份 | 22MB | ✅ 已上传 |\n| sessions（对话日志） | 5.1MB | ❌ 未备份 |\n| lcm.db | 1.4MB | ❌ 未备份 |\n| media/ | 4.1MB | ❌ 未备份 |\n| OpenViking | 4.6MB | ❌ 未备份 |\n| **合计** | **~37MB** | |\n\nGitHub 私有仓库不花钱，空间足够。**更完整的方案：**\n\n**全量备份方案：**\n- 用 **Git LFS** 存二进制（lcm.db、media、sessions）\n- 加上 OpenViking 的 session 和向量数据\n- credentials/ 和 .env 密钥仍然排除\n\n这样所有数据都有备份，只有密钥不在。\n\n**或者更保守方案：**\n- 只备份到 OpenViking 为止（不含 media）\n- media 太大了且没那么关键\n\n你想哪个？或者先把 OpenViking 加进来？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":40136,"output":572,"cacheRead":12505,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53213,"cost":{"input":0.012040799999999999,"output":0.0006864,"cacheRead":0.0007503,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0134775}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775448799523,"responseId":"062265e0b452b328910eee299f7c8dce"}}
