{"type":"message","id":"38fa09e7","parentId":"b2e1fb23","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:17:39.790Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"GitHub reports size as 0 for cloned repos in this API response. The actual repo size on disk is 22MB. Let me check if Git LFS is set up for this repo.\n\nActually, GitHub LFS has storage limits (1GB free for free accounts). Let me estimate:\n- Current backup: 22MB\n- Adding: sessions (5.1MB) + lcm.db (1.4MB) + media (4.1MB) + openviking (4.6MB) = ~15MB more\n- Total would be ~37MB, well within 1GB limit\n\nSo I can just add these files directly without Git LFS. \n\nLFS would be overkill for this size. Let me update the backup script to include everything except credentials/ and extensions/, and make sure openclaw.json is properly masked.","thinkingSignature":"71ed2bccf22550fdfc14ca4b71ee9290a429bb61aacb0bdfa3eff88cc2a4fcb8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gvtfsm6i09xb_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw 全量备份脚本 v2\n# 备份到 GitHub（增量），添加日期标签\n\nset -e\n\nREPO_DIR=\"/tmp/openclaw-backup-git\"\nSOURCE_OPENCLAW=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nSOURCE_OPENVIKING=\"$HOME/.openviking\"\nREPO=\"https://github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git\"\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n\n# 克隆或更新仓库\nif [ -d \"$REPO_DIR/.git\" ]; then\n    cd \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    git pull --quiet origin main\nelse\n    rm -rf \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    git clone --depth 1 \"$REPO\" \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    cd \"$REPO_DIR\"\nfi\n\n# 同步 OpenClaw 配置文件（脱敏）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='credentials' \\\n    --exclude='logs' \\\n    --exclude='extensions' \\\n    --exclude='subagents' \\\n    --exclude='tasks/runs.sqlite' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/openclaw.json\" ./\n\n# 脱敏 openclaw.json\nif [ -f openclaw.json ]; then\n    python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('openclaw.json') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\ndef mask(obj):\n    if isinstance(obj, dict):\n        for k in obj:\n            if k in ('token', 'apiKey', 'password', 'secret', 'socketToken'):\n                obj[k] = '***REDACTED***'\n            else:\n                mask(obj[k])\n    elif isinstance(obj, list):\n        for i in obj:\n            mask(i)\nmask(d)\nwith open('openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2)\n\" 2>/dev/null || true\nfi\n\n# 同步 workspace（含记忆、skills、agents、cron、identity）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace/\" \"./workspace/\"\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace-main/\" \"./workspace-main/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace-selector/\" \"./workspace-selector/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='*.db' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-shm' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-wal' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/agents/\" \"./agents/\"\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/cron/\" \"./cron/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/identity/\" \"./identity/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='*.db' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-shm' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-wal' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/flows/\" \"./flows/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/devices/\" \"./devices/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/delivery-queue/\" \"./delivery-queue/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='memory/lancedb-pro' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/memory/\" \"./memory/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 同步 skills\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='node_modules' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/skills/\" \"./skills/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 同步 OpenViking 关键数据（不含 _system 和 bot）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='_system' \\\n    --exclude='bot' \\\n    --exclude='.openviking.pid' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENVIKING/\" \"./openviking/\"\n\n# 提交\ngit add -A\nif git diff --cached --quiet; then\n    echo \"[$TODAY] No changes\"\nelse\n    git commit -m \"Full backup $TODAY\"\n    git push --quiet origin main\n    git tag -a \"backup-$TODAY\" -m \"Full backup $TODAY\"\n    git push origin \"backup-$TODAY\" --quiet\n    echo \"[$TODAY] Backup complete\"\nfi\n","path":"/tmp/openclaw-full-backup.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41509,"output":1182,"cacheRead":12505,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55196,"cost":{"input":0.012452699999999999,"output":0.0014184,"cacheRead":0.0007503,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0146214}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775449040174,"responseId":"062266d020b2a699d9be3d72204123e5"}}
