{"type":"message","id":"01be7abf","parentId":"86b9e528","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:40:18.621Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. The \"TK选品大师\" is configured as a Feishu account in the OpenClaw config:\n\n```json\n\"tts\": {\n  \"appId\": \"cli_a930f78f51399bc6\",\n  \"appSecret\": \"XEaTxDHuKHymRbRBlv6jvdUjPALqz4Ua\",\n  \"name\": \"TK 选品大师\",\n  \"enabled\": true\n}\n```\n\nAnd it's bound to the `tts` agent:\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  {\n    \"agentId\": \"tts\",\n    \"match\": {\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"accountId\": \"tts\"\n    }\n  }\n]\n```\n\nThe `tts` agent has:\n- Agent ID: `tts`\n- Name: `TTS-选品专家`\n- Workspace: `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-selector`\n- Agent dir: `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent`\n\nThe user is asking about:\n1. Current product acquisition status (现有情况)\n2. How to optimize going forward (后续怎么优化)\n\nFrom the memory files, I can see that on 2026-03-27, a `tts_hair_scout` agent was created with:\n- A skill called `tts_hair_scout` in the workspace skills\n- Scheduled to run daily at 10:00 AM\n- Uses TikTok scraping, LLM scoring, and ROI calculation\n- Results written to Bitable\n\nLet me look at the workspace-selector directory to understand what the tts agent has.","thinkingSignature":"fc6a46bb092f2fa49e34d1b4903ae66216ae1ea16ad185c5c03465827b1e5cfe"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eomw74fylniw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-selector/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39814,"output":394,"cacheRead":12848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53056,"cost":{"input":0.0119442,"output":0.0004728,"cacheRead":0.0007708799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01318788}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775457608234,"responseId":"06228849e3a0ded564b1f86196b0ec51"}}
