{"type":"message","id":"8a314398","parentId":"f6e9be19","timestamp":"2026-04-06T07:01:14.510Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4yg25jjimiwp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122) — I keep secrets like a vault... unless you print them in debug logs again.\n\nUsage: openclaw backup [options] [command]\n\nCreate and verify local backup archives for OpenClaw state\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  create      Write a backup archive for config, credentials, sessions, and\n              workspaces\n  help        Display help for command\n  verify      Validate a backup archive and its embedded manifest\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/backup"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1205,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122) — I keep secrets like a vault... unless you print them in debug logs again.\n\nUsage: openclaw backup [options] [command]\n\nCreate and verify local backup archives for OpenClaw state\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  create      Write a backup archive for config, credentials, sessions, and\n              workspaces\n  help        Display help for command\n  verify      Validate a backup archive and its embedded manifest\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/backup","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775458874501}}
