{"type":"message","id":"1c7fd713","parentId":"1ff1569f","timestamp":"2026-04-06T07:01:18.217Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_197gptrju5tv_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122) — Your config is valid, your assumptions are not.\n\nUsage: openclaw backup create [options]\n\nWrite a backup archive for config, credentials, sessions, and workspaces\n\nOptions:\n  --dry-run               Print the backup plan without writing the archive\n                          (default: false)\n  -h, --help              Display help for command\n  --json                  Output JSON (default: false)\n  --no-include-workspace  Exclude workspace directories from the backup\n  --only-config           Back up only the active JSON config file (default:\n                          false)\n  --output <path>         Archive path or destination directory\n  --verify                Verify the archive after writing it (default: false)\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw backup create\n    Create a timestamped backup in the current directory.\n  openclaw backup create --output ~/Backups\n    Write the archive into an existing backup directory.\n  openclaw backup create --dry-run --json\n    Preview the archive plan without writing any files.\n  openclaw backup create --verify\n    Create the archive and immediately validate its manifest and payload layout.\n  openclaw backup create --no-include-workspace\n    Back up state/config without agent workspace files.\n  openclaw backup create --only-config\n    Back up only the active JSON config file."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1209,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122) — Your config is valid, your assumptions are not.\n\nUsage: openclaw backup create [options]\n\nWrite a backup archive for config, credentials, sessions, and workspaces\n\nOptions:\n  --dry-run               Print the backup plan without writing the archive\n                          (default: false)\n  -h, --help              Display help for command\n  --json                  Output JSON (default: false)\n  --no-include-workspace  Exclude workspace directories from the backup\n  --only-config           Back up only the active JSON config file (default:\n                          false)\n  --output <path>         Archive path or destination directory\n  --verify                Verify the archive after writing it (default: false)\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw backup create\n    Create a timestamped backup in the current directory.\n  openclaw backup create --output ~/Backups\n    Write the archive into an existing backup directory.\n  openclaw backup create --dry-run --json\n    Preview the archive plan without writing any files.\n  openclaw backup create --verify\n    Create the archive and immediately validate its manifest and payload layout.\n  openclaw backup create --no-include-workspace\n    Back up state/config without agent workspace files.\n  openclaw backup create --only-config\n    Back up only the active JSON config file.","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775458878209}}
