n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")\n","name":"openclaw cron"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775469086902}}
{"type":"message","id":"edd98fd1","parentId":"5f9ce09d","timestamp":"2026-04-06T09:51:35.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to schedule a one-time job at tomorrow 10 AM Asia/Shanghai. The timezone is `Asia/Shanghai`. Let me use `--at` with an ISO datetime. Tomorrow 2026-04-07 at 10:00 AM would be `2026-04-07T10:00:00+08:00`.\n\nOr I can use a cron expression: `0 10 * * *` with `--tz Asia/Shanghai`.\n\nSince it's a one-time check, I'll use `--at` with the datetime. Let me use `--delete-after-run` so it doesn't persist.\n\nThe command should be:\n```\nopenclaw cron add --name \"openviking数据检查\" --message \"检查OpenViking数据写入是否正常，告诉我结果\" --at \"2026-04-07T10:00:00+08:00\" --tz Asia/Shanghai --delete-after-run\n```\n\nActually, let me think about what message to send. The agent job will receive this message and I want it to report back. Let me construct this carefully.","thinkingSignature":"4e8722b91390918f21f31b6aba0aea915af6a0ed4b0b0c8bef877576d9c71544"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e0tyoxr1if6x_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"openviking数据检查\" \\\n  --message \"请检查OpenViking的数据写入是否正常。验证方法：1) 查看localhost:1933是否有响应 2) 检查openviking日志有无写入记录 3) 尝试写入一条测试数据。完成后直接向我报告结果。\" \\\n  --at \"2026-04-07T10:00:00+08:00\" \\\n  --tz \"Asia/Shanghai\" \\\n  --delete-after-run \\\n  --announce \\\n  --channel feishu \\\n  --account kiit \\\n  --timeout-seconds 60 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7324,"output":380,"cacheRead":12933,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20637,"cost":{"input":0.0021972,"output":0.00045599999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0007759799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034291799999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775469086912,"responseId":"0622b51f5991abbdaa1d1bdb1f1ae9a7"}}
