{"type":"message","id":"e346091d","parentId":"b5d36d53","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:00:47.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Weather skill works perfectly. Let me report back to the user.","thinkingSignature":"740d2cd0b9206f071addd877336848e1a68022094d7702c00159c6851c348696"},{"type":"text","text":"Weather skill 正常 ✅\n\n**上海当前天气：** ☀️ +20°C（体感 +20°C），西南风 21km/h，湿度 68%\n\n调用方式是通过 `curl wttr.in/<城市>`，不需要 API key，响应很快。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":12250,"output":69,"cacheRead":12933,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25252,"cost":{"input":0.003675,"output":0.0000828,"cacheRead":0.0007759799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004533779999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775476844460,"responseId":"0622d36cdc000be264aa274dd6ecab4d"}}
